609
00:38:58,260 --> 00:39:00,300
[SPEAKER_01] a moj Damjan priča, hoda, trči.

610
00:39:00,760 --> 00:39:03,400
[SPEAKER_00] Vidjela sam ga da, ujutro prije, da.

611
00:39:03,400 --> 00:39:06,539
