837
00:46:17,840 --> 00:46:19,280
[SPEAKER_01] tko zna kako bih ja bila.

838
00:46:20,380 --> 00:46:27,619
[SPEAKER_00] Da ima smisla boriti se,

839
00:46:27,619 --> 00:46:30,699
[SPEAKER_00] ima smisla boriti se za drugoga,

840
00:46:30,699 --> 00:46:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] baviti se s drugim,

841
00:46:32,460 --> 00:46:33,500
[SPEAKER_00] biti tu za tog drugog,

842
00:46:33,500 --> 00:46:34,699
[SPEAKER_00] to je u ovom zločaju dijete,

843
00:46:34,699 --> 00:46:37,360
[SPEAKER_00] u nekim drugim zločajima je to netko drugi,

844
00:46:37,360 --> 00:46:39,659
[SPEAKER_00] i konačnici,

845
00:46:39,659 --> 00:46:40,280
[SPEAKER_00] ovo što ste rekli,

846
00:46:40,280 --> 00:46:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] taj primjer,

847
00:46:41,480 --> 00:46:44,500
[SPEAKER_00] primjer konkretan osobe u toj situaciji

848
00:46:44,500 --> 00:46:46,239
[SPEAKER_00] koja je tu situaciju odživjela

849
00:46:46,239 --> 00:46:48,719
[SPEAKER_00] na onaj način na koju vi želite odživjeti.

850
00:46:48,719 --> 00:46:53,340
[SPEAKER_00] I to je meni bio potice

851
00:46:53,340 --> 00:46:56,300
[SPEAKER_00] za razgovore sa ženama poput vas,

852
00:46:56,300 --> 00:46:58,340
[SPEAKER_00] jer mislim da se nedovoljno čuju

853
00:46:58,340 --> 00:47:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] ti konkretni primjeri,

854
00:47:00,000 --> 00:47:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] i evo dokaz,

855
00:47:01,039 --> 00:47:01,920
[SPEAKER_00] živi ste vi,

856
00:47:01,920 --> 00:47:03,739
[SPEAKER_00] da se to može izdržati,

857
00:47:03,739 --> 00:47:04,940
[SPEAKER_00] i da nas to,

858
00:47:04,940 --> 00:47:06,239
[SPEAKER_00] koliko god danas boli,

859
00:47:06,239 --> 00:47:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] može i oplemeniti u konačnici,

860
00:47:07,960 --> 00:47:09,119
[SPEAKER_00] to je ono što ste mi rekli,

861
00:47:09,119 --> 00:47:10,760
[SPEAKER_00] da ste vi danas bolja osoba,

862
00:47:10,760 --> 00:47:12,800
[SPEAKER_00] jača osoba nego što ste bili.

863
00:47:13,400 --> 00:47:15,960
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je i skoro sam drugačija,

864
00:47:15,960 --> 00:47:17,739
[SPEAKER_01] znači imam osjećaj da je

865
00:47:17,739 --> 00:47:19,940
[SPEAKER_01] od mene otišlo,

866
00:47:19,940 --> 00:47:20,539
[SPEAKER_01] kako da kažem,

867
00:47:20,539 --> 00:47:21,440
[SPEAKER_01] jako kao ljuske,

868
00:47:21,440 --> 00:47:24,820
[SPEAKER_01] otpalo ono što je bilo nezrelo,

869
00:47:24,820 --> 00:47:27,300
[SPEAKER_01] što je bilo nebitno,

870
00:47:27,300 --> 00:47:29,420
[SPEAKER_01] što mi se nametalo ne zato što sam htjela,

871
00:47:29,420 --> 00:47:31,019
[SPEAKER_01] nego zato što sam dio društva.

872
00:47:32,019 --> 00:47:33,139
[SPEAKER_01] određenim trenucima,

873
00:47:33,139 --> 00:47:33,699
[SPEAKER_01] kad dođete,

874
00:47:33,699 --> 00:47:35,980
[SPEAKER_01] doživite neko stanje,

875
00:47:35,980 --> 00:47:37,159
[SPEAKER_01] vam uistinu neke stvari

876
00:47:37,159 --> 00:47:38,199
[SPEAKER_01] prestanu biti bitne.

877
00:47:38,199 --> 00:47:39,159
[SPEAKER_01] Biti važne, tako,

878
00:47:39,159 --> 00:47:40,440
[SPEAKER_00] jer vidite da nisu bitne.

879
00:47:40,440 --> 00:47:42,380
[SPEAKER_01] Tako, ali uostalom,

880
00:47:42,380 --> 00:47:44,699
