881
00:47:44,699 --> 00:47:46,579
[SPEAKER_01] nameću bitne.

882
00:47:46,579 --> 00:47:47,960
[SPEAKER_01] Dobre su,

883
00:47:47,960 --> 00:47:48,460
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći.

884
00:47:48,460 --> 00:47:49,300
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, razumijem.

885
00:47:49,300 --> 00:47:51,099
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu u onom smislu,

886
00:47:51,099 --> 00:47:52,440
[SPEAKER_01] kako vam se predstavlja.

887
00:47:52,440 --> 00:47:54,079
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu toliko bitne.

888
00:47:54,079 --> 00:47:55,920
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je, u onom smislu,

889
00:47:55,920 --> 00:47:57,559
[SPEAKER_01] evo ja ću krenuti od banalnog primjera,

890
00:47:57,559 --> 00:47:58,440
[SPEAKER_01] kao žena,

891
00:47:58,440 --> 00:47:59,860
[SPEAKER_01] to je banalni primjer,

892
00:48:00,000 --> 00:48:02,460
[SPEAKER_01] premda je kompleksno.

893
00:48:02,460 --> 00:48:03,980
[SPEAKER_01] Žena mora držati do sebe.

894
00:48:03,980 --> 00:48:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onako, gledajte,

895
00:48:05,000 --> 00:48:06,639
[SPEAKER_01] moje dijete umire,

896
00:48:06,639 --> 00:48:07,440
[SPEAKER_01] mene boli briga,

897
00:48:07,440 --> 00:48:09,239
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam ja u majici,

898
00:48:09,239 --> 00:48:10,099
[SPEAKER_01] u haljini,

899
00:48:10,099 --> 00:48:11,780
[SPEAKER_01] s noktima, bez noktiju.

900
00:48:11,780 --> 00:48:12,400
[SPEAKER_01] Razumijete?

901
00:48:12,400 --> 00:48:13,420
[SPEAKER_01] U tom trenutku,

902
00:48:13,420 --> 00:48:14,739
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja sam i dalje žena.

903
00:48:14,739 --> 00:48:16,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ja držim do sebe.

904
00:48:16,139 --> 00:48:16,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ja držim,

905
00:48:16,599 --> 00:48:17,860
[SPEAKER_01] ja trebam nekog da mi polu.

906
00:48:17,860 --> 00:48:18,400
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, recimo,

907
00:48:18,400 --> 00:48:19,659
[SPEAKER_01] banalan primjer,

908
00:48:19,659 --> 00:48:20,219
[SPEAKER_01] razumijete?

909
00:48:20,219 --> 00:48:23,179
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam imala stage

910
00:48:23,179 --> 00:48:24,260
[SPEAKER_01] ustati iz kreveta,

911
00:48:24,260 --> 00:48:25,079
[SPEAKER_01] od stresa,

912
00:48:25,079 --> 00:48:26,559
[SPEAKER_01] od svega što se meni događa.

913
00:48:26,559 --> 00:48:28,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam znala što se događa.

914
00:48:30,000 --> 00:48:30,679
[SPEAKER_01] Kako pričam,

915
00:48:30,679 --> 00:48:33,099
[SPEAKER_01] što jednostavno stres se dogodio

916
00:48:33,099 --> 00:48:34,440
[SPEAKER_01] i poslije kad smo mi došli kući.

917
00:48:34,440 --> 00:48:36,300
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je trebala ogromna podrška.

918
00:48:36,300 --> 00:48:37,539
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je trebalo nekog

919
00:48:37,539 --> 00:48:38,659
[SPEAKER_01] ko će mi reći,

920
00:48:38,659 --> 00:48:39,559
[SPEAKER_01] ti si učiteljica,

921
