[SPEAKER_01] boli me briga kakva hodam po gradu.

924
00:48:43,340 --> 00:48:45,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ja pokušavam se izboriti

925
00:48:45,579 --> 00:48:47,059
[SPEAKER_01] za sad, za svoj život.

926
00:48:47,059 --> 00:48:49,300
[SPEAKER_01] Pokušavam naći sebe drugačiju,

927
00:48:49,300 --> 00:48:51,480
[SPEAKER_01] smijestiti u društvu u kojem jesam.

928
00:48:51,679 --> 00:48:53,139
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, jer ja više nisam ista.

929
00:48:53,139 --> 00:48:54,300
[SPEAKER_01] I ne mogu biti ista

930
00:48:54,300 --> 00:48:55,599
[SPEAKER_01] i ne želim biti ista.

931
00:48:55,599 --> 00:48:58,179
[SPEAKER_01] Taj, recimo, dio i poslje

932
00:48:58,179 --> 00:48:59,300
[SPEAKER_01] gdje čovjek treba

933
00:48:59,300 --> 00:49:00,820
[SPEAKER_01] i žene trebaju podršku.

934
00:49:00,820 --> 00:49:01,360
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da.

935
00:49:01,360 --> 00:49:03,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što sam isto primijetila,

936
