[SPEAKER_01] znači,

937
00:49:04,199 --> 00:49:06,059
[SPEAKER_01] u svakom gradu imaju ustanove,

938
00:49:06,059 --> 00:49:07,519
[SPEAKER_01] škole,

939
00:49:07,519 --> 00:49:09,139
[SPEAKER_01] djece sa poteškoćama

940
00:49:09,139 --> 00:49:10,079
[SPEAKER_01] s posljednim potrebama.

941
00:49:10,079 --> 00:49:10,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

942
