[SPEAKER_01] ti roditelji žive s nama.

944
00:49:12,940 --> 00:49:14,260
[SPEAKER_01] To smo mi,

945
00:49:14,260 --> 00:49:15,440
[SPEAKER_01] to su naša djeca.

946
00:49:15,440 --> 00:49:16,840
[SPEAKER_01] Oni nisu ništa drugačiji.

947
00:49:17,900 --> 00:49:18,360
[SPEAKER_01] Jednostavno,

948
00:49:18,360 --> 00:49:19,320
[SPEAKER_01] svi jednako vrijedni.

949
00:49:19,320 --> 00:49:20,039
[SPEAKER_00] Da, i trebaju,

950
00:49:20,039 --> 00:49:21,300
[SPEAKER_00] i trebaju ono što ste...

951
00:49:21,300 --> 00:49:22,840
[SPEAKER_01] Moje djete je bilo sa tumorom

952
00:49:22,840 --> 00:49:24,239
[SPEAKER_01] i moje djete je bez tumora.

953
00:49:24,239 --> 00:49:25,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ali moje djete je moje djete.

954
00:49:25,659 --> 00:49:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ono je jednako vrijedno.

955
00:49:27,000 --> 00:49:28,219
[SPEAKER_01] Ako me shvaćate.

956
00:49:28,219 --> 00:49:29,119
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno.

957
00:49:29,119 --> 00:49:29,440
[SPEAKER_01] Evo,

958
00:49:29,440 --> 00:49:31,039
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam da bi se izrazila.

959
00:49:31,039 --> 00:49:32,280
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da ste dobro.

960
00:49:32,280 --> 00:49:33,719
[SPEAKER_00] Jako izrazili puno vam hvala

961
00:49:33,719 --> 00:49:34,739
[SPEAKER_00] na ovom razgovoru.

962
00:49:34,739 --> 00:49:36,780
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam uvjirena

963
00:49:36,780 --> 00:49:38,559
[SPEAKER_00] da će ovo vaše iskustvo,

964
00:49:38,559 --> 00:49:39,880
[SPEAKER_00] kao što je vama pomogla,

965
