[SPEAKER_00] vaša lavica,

966
00:49:40,579 --> 00:49:42,260
[SPEAKER_00] da ćete vi moći pomoći

967
00:49:42,260 --> 00:49:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] mnogim drugim ženama

968
00:49:44,119 --> 00:49:46,219
[SPEAKER_00] sa ovim što ste podijelili.

969
00:49:46,219 --> 00:49:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] Trebaju gledatelji puno vam hvala

970
00:49:47,960 --> 00:49:49,239
[SPEAKER_00] da ste pratili,

971
00:49:49,239 --> 00:49:50,719
[SPEAKER_00] da me pratite.

972
00:49:50,719 --> 00:49:54,800
[SPEAKER_00] I nadam se da će vam

973
00:49:54,800 --> 00:49:56,880
[SPEAKER_00] ova tema vas obogatiti

974
00:49:56,880 --> 00:49:58,159
