978
00:50:01,739 --> 00:50:02,960
[SPEAKER_00] Marina, doviđenja.

979
00:50:02,960 --> 00:50:04,880
[SPEAKER_01] Doviđenja, doviđenja.

980
00:50:04,880 --> 00:50:05,500
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vama.

981
00:50:05,500 --> 00:50:34,360
[SPEAKER_01] Doviđenja, doviđenja.

